        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-red-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-red-700">‚ö´ Black Lichen Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Dark spots and patches that are resistant to normal cleaning methods.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-red-600">‚úì Professional removal without damage</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-700">üí® Atmospheric Staining</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">General discoloration from pollution, traffic fumes and environmental factors.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-600">‚úì Deep clean restores original colour</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-yellow-700">üï∏Ô∏è Spider Webs & Debris</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Accumulated webs, dirt and organic matter in soffit areas.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-yellow-600">‚úì Thorough cleaning of all crevices</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
