          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Organic matter trapped behind gutters and in bracket areas.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-purple-600">‚úì Complete removal and clean-up</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-orange-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-700">üíß Water Stain Marks</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calcium deposits and water marks from overflowing gutters.</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-orange-600">‚úì Specialist removal techniques</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </WidgetWrapper>

  <!-- Why Not DIY -->
  <WidgetWrapper>
    <section class="py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-8 border border-amber-200">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6 text-amber-900">Why Professional Cleaning Beats DIY</h2>
