              <li>‚Ä¢ Inadequate pressure washing results</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Time-consuming and physically demanding</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Risk of property damage</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Limited access to high areas</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-green-800">‚úÖ Professional Advantages:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-700">
