              <li>‚Ä¢ Specialist UPVC cleaning products</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Professional pressure washing equipment</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Fast, efficient service</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Fully insured for peace of mind</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Access to all roof areas safely</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </WidgetWrapper>

  <!-- Maintenance Schedule -->
  <WidgetWrapper>
    <section class="py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Recommended Cleaning Schedule</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-900">üè† Standard Properties</h3>
          <div class="text-blue-800">
            <p class="font-medium mb-2">Every 2-3 Years</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Properties in normal environments with average exposure to algae and atmospheric pollution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-900">üå≤ High-Risk Areas</h3>
          <div class="text-green-800">
            <p class="font-medium mb-2">Every 1-2 Years</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Properties near trees, rural areas, or exposed to high moisture where algae grows faster.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-purple-900">üèòÔ∏è Urban Areas</h3>
          <div class="text-purple-800">
            <p class="font-medium mb-2">Every 2-4 Years</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Urban properties may need less frequent cleaning but benefit from pollution stain removal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </WidgetWrapper>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <FAQs
    title="Fascia & Soffit Cleaning FAQs"
    subtitle="Everything you need to know about professional UPVC roofline cleaning"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Will pressure washing damage my UPVC?',
        description: 'No, we use controlled pressure appropriate for UPVC and specialist techniques that clean effectively without causing damage. DIY pressure washing is where damage typically occurs.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How long does fascia and soffit cleaning take?',
        description: 'Typically 2-4 hours depending on property size and level of staining. We work efficiently to minimise disruption while ensuring thorough results.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Can you clean coloured UPVC or just white?',
        description: 'We clean all colours of UPVC including white, cream, brown, and grey. Our methods are safe for all UPVC types and finishes.',
      },
      {
        title: 'What if the staining comes back quickly?',
        description: 'Properly cleaned UPVC should stay clean for 2-3 years in normal conditions. Quick return of staining usually indicates underlying moisture issues we can advise on.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do you clean inside soffits and fascias?',
        description: 'This is an exterior cleaning service. We clean the visible external surfaces of fascias, soffits, and gutters. For internal gutter clearing (inside the gutters), we offer a separate Gutter Clearing service using high-reach vacuum systems.',
